Source: libflagfft
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: FlagOS Contributors <contact@flagos.io>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13),
               cmake (>= 3.18),
               ninja-build,
               patchelf,
               python3-dev,
               libsqlite3-dev,
               nlohmann-json3-dev (>= 3.11.3)
# fmt is intentionally NOT in Build-Depends. Ubuntu 24.04's
# libfmt-dev is 9.1.0 but libtriton_jit requires 10.2.1, so the build
# pulls fmt 10.2.1 via CMake FetchContent and bundles it into
# libflagfft.so. See debian/rules override_dh_auto_configure.
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/flagos-ai/FlagFFT
Vcs-Browser: https://github.com/flagos-ai/FlagFFT
Vcs-Git: https://github.com/flagos-ai/FlagFFT.git
Rules-Requires-Root: no
X-Build-Environment: This package is designed to be built in a CUDA container
 environment that provides the necessary SDK and Python packages:
 .
 - CUDA toolkit (>= 12.0) from nvidia/cuda base image
 - PyTorch (>= 2.5.0) and Triton (>= 3.1.0) via pip (required by the
   bundled libtriton_jit submodule built statically into libflagfft.so)
 - pybind11 via pip; SQLite3 + nlohmann-json via system packages
 - fmt 10.2.1 downloaded via CMake FetchContent at build time
 .
 The Build-Depends listed above are for the Debian packaging tools only.
 CUDA and Python deps are provided by the container environment.

Package: libflagfft-nvidia
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: FlagFFT — C++ FFT library for FlagOS (NVIDIA backend)
 FlagFFT is a cuFFT-style FFT library with Triton/TLE code generation,
 targeting FlagOS multi-vendor accelerators. The NVIDIA backend uses
 CUDA + Triton-JIT for kernel generation.
 .
 This package contains the shared library libflagfft.so built for
 NVIDIA hardware. libtriton_jit is bundled statically into this
 library; no separate libtriton-jit runtime dependency.

Package: libflagfft-nvidia-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libflagfft-nvidia (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: FlagFFT development files (NVIDIA backend)
 FlagFFT is a cuFFT-style FFT library with Triton/TLE code generation.
 .
 This package contains the header files for building applications
 against libflagfft-nvidia.
